Show current database connections:
sql
Copy code
SHOW PROCESSLIST;
Display server status:
sql
Copy code
SHOW STATUS;
View current running queries:
sql
Copy code
SELECT * FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.PROCESSLIST WHERE COMMAND != 'Sleep';
Check database size:
sql
Copy code
SELECT table_schema "Database Name", SUM(data_length + index_length) / 1024 / 1024 "Database Size (MB)" FROM information_schema.tables GROUP BY table_schema;
List active threads:
sql
Copy code
SHOW ENGINE INNODB STATUS;
Check table fragmentation:
sql
Copy code
SHOW TABLE STATUS;
View slow queries:
sql
Copy code
SHOW VARIABLES LIKE 'slow_query_log';
Analyze slow query log:
sql
Copy code
SHOW VARIABLES LIKE 'long_query_time';
Check index usage:
sql
Copy code
